Opening soon…So this project has been taken a huge amount of effort from many. And I thank the @poloclubofbocaraton for trusting me to create & design such a rare space that no other club will have. Custom coffee blends, beautiful house-made croissants, cakes, chocolates, ice creams, pastries, in-house honey, smoothies, and gifting. Luxurious packaging and presentations all designed and picked out by me. It’s a passion project indeed. So excited to show you all more….
